  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink249-kilavi">vēlaṉ kūṟiya māṟṟattai meyyeṉak koṇṭa tāy kēṭpat talaimakaṭkut tōḻi kūṟiyatu. </p>
        <p xml:lang="en">What the confidante told the heroine, so that the mother listens—the mother who took as true the change spoken by the Vēlaṉ.
  
          
          
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink249">
<l>peymmaṇal varaippiṟ kaḻaṅkupaṭut taṉṉaikku</l>
<l>murukeṉa moḻiyum vēlaṉ maṟṟavaṉ</l>
<l>vāḻiya vilaṅku maruvic</l>
<l>cūrmalai nāṭaṉai yaṟiyā tōṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>That Vēlaṉ priest,</l>
        <l>who, having spread Molucca beans</l>
        <l>within the bounds of the poured sand,</l>
        <l>says “Muruku” to mother—</l>
        <l>may he, moreover, live long—</l>
        <l rend="space">he who does not know</l>
        <l>the man from the land</l>
        <l>of the fearsome mountain</l>
        <l>with glimmering waterfalls!</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
